            "title": "特朗普關稅戰｜特朗普據報促藥廠返美生產　港股藥明系今跌一成",
            "description": "<div class=\"caas-body\"><figure class=\"caas-figure\"><div class=\"caas-figure-with-pb\" style=\"max-height: 640px\"><div><div class=\"caas-img-container\" style=\"padding-bottom:67%\"><img alt=\"特朗普據報要求藥廠把生產搬回美國，否則會面臨關稅。(AP)\" class=\"caas-img has-preview\" data-src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nN3JkThELcmC8YHIHGsp1g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/am730_578/ee3d5626f53146949734c730caa0af18\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nN3JkThELcmC8YHIHGsp1g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/am730_578/ee3d5626f53146949734c730caa0af18\"/></div></div></div><div class=\"caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image\"><figcaption class=\"caption-collapse\">特朗普據報要求藥廠把生產搬回美國，否則會面臨關稅。(AP)</figcaption></div></figure><p><span><span><span><span><span>《彭博》報道，美國總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/tag/特朗普\">特朗普</a>在一次私人會議上警告製藥公司，表示關稅即將到來，要求企業盡快將海外生產轉移到美國。受到消息影響，港股藥明系今日(24)急挫，截止發稿，藥明康德(港交所：2359)及藥明生物(港交所：2269)跌約一成，分別低見62.4元及23.1元，</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>是今日表現最差的藍籌。</span></span></span></span></span></p><figure class=\"caas-figure\"><div class=\"caas-figure-with-pb\" style=\"max-height: 484px\"><div><div class=\"caas-img-container caas-img-loader\" style=\"padding-bottom:50%\"><img alt=\"受到消息影響，港股藥明系今日急挫。(資料圖片)\" class=\"caas-img caas-lazy has-preview\" data-src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8Duen2AMfMFZAvUqwG2L5A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ4NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/am730_578/b4c3bdce71e0a61535d9679880b908ff\"/><noscript><img alt=\"受到消息影響，港股藥明系今日急挫。(資料圖片)\" class=\"caas-img\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8Duen2AMfMFZAvUqwG2L5A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ4NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/am730_578/b4c3bdce71e0a61535d9679880b908ff\"/></noscript></div></div></div><div class=\"caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image\"><figcaption class=\"caption-collapse\">受到消息影響，港股藥明系今日急挫。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><h2><span><span><span><span><span>上周會見禮來默沙東輝瑞等高層</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p><span><span><span><span><span>《彭博》的報道提到，特朗普上周四(20日)在白宮會見多間製藥企業的高層，</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>包括禮來(美：LLY)、默沙東(美：MRK)、輝瑞(美：PFE)的行政總裁，以及行業游說組織的負責人。這些藥廠高層原本希望說服特朗普支持縮減一項允許聯邦政府對某些藥品價格進行談判的法律，並支持遏制中間商的政策。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span><span><span><span><span>然而，報道引述消息指，特朗普沒有作出承諾，僅表示擔心調整藥品定價政策可能會使共和黨通過稅改的努力變得更加複雜。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p>原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/特朗普關稅戰-特朗普據報促藥廠返美生產-港股藥明系今跌一成/535588?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/特朗普關稅戰-特朗普據報促藥廠返美生產-港股藥明系今跌一成/535588?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/特朗普關稅戰-特朗普據報促藥廠返美生產-港股藥明系今跌一成/535588?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E6%88%B0-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E4%BF%83%E8%97%A5%E5%BB%A0%E8%BF%94%E7%BE%8E%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E8%97%A5%E6%98%8E%E7%B3%BB%E4%BB%8A%E8%B7%8C-%E6%88%90-072000441.html",
